name: User tries to purchase CWS at store with Mobile Payments and Car Wash subscriptions and no CWS features in foreign BU
description: CWS flow when at a store with no car wash at foreign BU
descriptionHtml: CWS flow when at a store with no car wash at foreign BU

testStage.description: CWS flow when at a store with no car wash at foreign BU

steps.name: I check that the Saucelabs session is preserved

parameters.name: userProfile
parameters.value: {PHONE_NUMBER=782782000, FIRST_NAME=Kamil, PASSWORD=#Test123, EMAIL=kamil.nowak@gmaptest.com, PHONE_COUNTRY_PREFIX=+48, PHONE_COUNTRY=Poland, OTP=000000, LAST_NAME=Nowak, BUSINESS_UNIT=DK}

steps.name: I skip linking my card
I mock the location of the device to "SWEDEN_NO_CAR_WASH"
I click on "ACCOUNT" button
I check that the "Account Screen" is displayed
I check that the "Profile" tab is displayed
I click on "BUILD NUMBER" tab
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I enter the location data of the "SWEDEN_NO_CAR_WASH" station
I check "Set Location" page is visible
I enter the site ID "SWEDEN_NO_CAR_WASH" in the input
I click on "SET LOCATION" button
I click on "Car Wash" advertisement
I check if "Car Wash" advertisement is displayed
I close and open application
I make sure that the location is set correctly
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
I check that the "CAR WASH" tab is displayed
I click on "CAR WASH" tab
I make sure that the "CAR WASH" tab is in the default state
I click on Car Wash "BEGIN CAR WASH" button
I check that the "Trying to access your subscription abroad?" is displayed
I get the text from the middle text area on the "Please note, subscriptions are valid only in the country of purchase. However, you can still buy single wash."

I check that the application text: "Please note, subscriptions are valid only in the country of purchase. However, you can still buy single wash." is equals to expected value: "Please note, subscriptions are valid only in the country of purchase. However, you can still buy single wash."

parameters.name: Actual:
parameters.value: Please note, subscriptions are valid only in the country of purchase. However, you can still buy single wash.

parameters.name: Expected:
parameters.value: Please note, subscriptions are valid only in the country of purchase. However, you can still buy single wash.

steps.name: I click on "GO BACK" button
I check that the "Home Screen" is displayed
